arch:property.oc:show_val: Accordoing to narrative, site is a prehisotirc shell mdden/mound that once had a house (historic or modern)structure on it and a covered well. Prehsitoric and historic artifacts recovered.
The site is significant for its large size and considerable depth and extent of deposits, this large, gently curved, ridge-shaped shell midden forms the core of Catfish Point.
